## Commercial Use Notice

This project is **open source with commercial intent**:

✅ **Free for personal and commercial use**
✅ **Source code available under MIT License**  
✅ **Commercial distribution allowed**
✅ **Attribution required** - Please include this copyright notice
✅ **Official paid version available** on Mac App Store

### Attribution Requirements

When using this code in your projects, please include:

1. **Copyright notice**: Include the MIT license text above
2. **Credit attribution**: "Based on Live Walls by Felipe [Tu Apellido]"
3. **Repository link**: https://github.com/[tu-usuario]/LiveWalls (when applicable)

### Dual Model

- **Open Source Version**: Full source code, MIT licensed, community-driven
- **Commercial Version**: Mac App Store distribution, official support, premium features

Both versions benefit the community - the open source version drives innovation,
while the commercial version funds continued development.

### Contributing

Contributions to the open source version are welcome and appreciated! 
Contributors help improve both the free and commercial versions.
